Severstal First-Quarter Crude Steel Output Declined 5%

-- B y   Y u l i y a   F e d o r i n o v a
-- 
2011-04-28T06:01:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-28/severstal-first-quarter-crude-steel-output-declined-5-.html
OAO Severstal, Russian billionaire
 Alexei Mordashov ’s steelmaker, said output of crude steel fell 5
percent in the first quarter from the previous three months to
3.65 million metric tons.  Gold sales at Severstal’s unit Nord Gold NV slipped 10
percent to 173,930 ounces.  To contact the reporters on this story: Yuliya Fedorinova in
Moscow at   yfedorinova@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story: Amanda Jordan
at   ajordan11@bloomberg.net . 